{"tid":1512092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女友多到數唔清！黃旭熙與同學玩一王兩后","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T22:14:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":15,"dislike":349,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6b11d080eea86480de7ef27a6e80ddea5d33fd","tid":1512092,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190828/photo/bkn-20190828000007611-0828_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190828000402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190828%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190828000007611-0828_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190828000402&h=df1c9688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生時期嘅黃旭熙已經好靚仔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190828/photo/bkn-20190828000007611-0828_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190828000402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190828%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190828000007611-0828_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190828000402&h=373f6df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n練咗一身肌肉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190828/photo/bkn-20190828000007611-0828_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190828000402\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190828%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190828000007611-0828_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190828000402&h=6f21c4d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃旭熙參與《奔跑吧》，「跑」出人氣！<br />\n<br />\n繼王嘉爾揚威內地後，另一港產小鮮肉黃旭熙（Lucas）同樣在內地發展得有聲有色，不過人紅是非多，走紅後即被網民爆出黑歷史，更有大量以往與女性的親密合照流出，可見他中學時期異性緣勁旺！<br />\n<br />\n近年不少香港藝人積極進軍內地市場，包括王嘉爾、陳偉霆等，而年僅20歲的韓團NCT香港籍成員黃旭熙，早前單獨亮相人氣內地綜藝節目《奔跑吧》，在節目中大晒港普而經常鬧出笑話，人氣因而急升。他於2015年參加SM事務所在港舉辦的全球選秀，成為旗下練習生，去年以韓團EXO的同門師弟組合NCT身份在韓國出道。<br />\n<br />\n有網民隨即大起底，中泰混血兒的Lucas在港土生土長，赴韓前曾就讀位於沙田的中學，讀書時期練得一身肌肉，加上外貌出眾，其個人社交網帳戶一度擁有逾萬名追蹤者，明顯是校內風頭躉！不過有網民指他的鼻形較以前立體，被質疑有整容之嫌，但也有粉絲認為只是化妝效果。<br />\n<br />\n前女友曾宣示主權<br />\n<br />\n現時風靡亞洲萬千少女心的Lucas，中學時期的異性緣也不容小覷。網上流出多張疑似他與前女友的親密照，其中一張更同時獲兩名女同學獻吻。Lucas出道成為韓星後，有網民發現其前女友曾在網上拍短片「宣示主權」，大批粉絲紛紛到女方社交網留言，她亦逐一回覆，表示替對方開心，但又指二人已再沒聯絡。此外，據指Lucas出道前已是一位韓迷，2015年曾出席韓國女星金所炫在港舉辦的粉絲見面會，當時他以小粉絲身份上台送禮物及索簽名。"},{"pid":"e319e274ea47519dfc03d77255bd99c7d359393d","tid":1512092,"uid":108040,"like":165,"dislike":1,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"Who fucking care"},{"pid":"a8df77ede96c661863ee1ead714c3c86cbcd38aa","tid":1512092,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":139,"score":-137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3x2cbC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3x2cbC.jpg&h=f2cdd0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNusoii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNusoii.jpg&h=ee2c5199&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODe77KY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODe77KY.jpg&h=1286a513&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSD1sKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSD1sKZ.jpg&h=aa726ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjXhLwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjXhLwE.jpg&h=609ce5c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHX9BDk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHX9BDk.jpg&h=8c3522ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkqZYRG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkqZYRG.jpg&h=49e825dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycshLwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycshLwH.jpg&h=f141fa5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ln9TiRH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLn9TiRH.jpg&h=002e39cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYzzNK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi